# Data Cleaning â€“ Customer Complaint Intelligence System

## Overview
This document details the pre-SQL data cleaning performed in Excel to standardize text fields, correct spelling errors, and handle invalid dates. Cleaned datasets were then imported into SQL Server for modeling and analysis.

---

## 1. Customers Table

**Standardized Regions and Corrected Invalid Entries**

| Original Value | Replacement       | Count |
|----------------|-----------------|-------|
| Latam          | Latin America   | 74    |
| Middleeast     | Middle-East     | 52    |
| Na             | North America   | 53    |
| Africa         | Africa          | 58    |
| Eu             | Europe          | 53    |
| invalid_date   | NULL            | 80    |

