## 3. Complaints Table

**Corrected Invalid Dates and Spelling Errors**

| Original Value | Replacement | Count |
|----------------|------------|-------|
| invalid_date   | NULL       | 303   |
| sycn           | sync       | 103   |
| Biling         | Billing    | 5,955 |

