## 4. Row Counts Post-Cleaning

| Table       | Rows    |
|-------------|--------|
| Complaints  | 50,000 |
| Resolutions | 39,846 |
| Customers   | 10,000 |

---

## 5. Notes

- Standardizing regions ensures accurate reporting and prevents fragmentation in dashboards.  
- Fixing spelling errors in complaints and resolutions enables reliable keyword-based sentiment scoring and urgency evaluation.  
- Invalid dates set to `NULL` allow correct time-based aggregations in SQL, such as risk scoring and complaint aging.  
- All cleaning steps were documented for traceability and reproducibility.
